{"tid":1045191,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"大家介賭未？自從我介左賭，人生真係唔同左。","createTime":"2019-03-03T12:21:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-04T09:00:04.000Z","uid":53062,"like":16,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8c90918450e717c0dcf8bd90848858a6a2d94d9d","tid":1045191,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T12:21:58.000Z","msg":"三個月前我成功介賭。到今日都未賭過一蚊 亦都冇左癮。<br />\n換黎既係我精神好左好多。因為唔使再半夜望實買左既賽事。<br />\n而且錢方面真係鬆動左好多。就好似上個月同女朋友行街。佢睇中左個3萬既袋，我可以即刻比錢買到。比着以前唔係話買唔到，但唔會即刻比又唔心痛。<br />\n同屋企人關係又好左，以前成日賭唔理佢地，佢地講左d輸字我又能脾氣。但呢家大家就有講有笑。仲成日比多點家用佢地用。<br />\n介左之後真係快樂左好多"},{"pid":"7faf95c78965329a3d7c584a3bb7a8efacaf045a","tid":1045191,"uid":21423,"like":17,"dislike":4,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T12:22:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ea44436a5510f840ee2c279b4927138c0476989b","tid":1045191,"uid":236401,"like":12,"dislike":3,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T12:23:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b7ebccd597b39adfe69d4e4c96c59d75e6c16a90","tid":1045191,"uid":44333,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ea44436a5510f840ee2c279b4927138c0476989b","tid":1045191,"uid":236401,"like":12,"dislike":3,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T12:23:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T03:36:46.000Z","msg":"其實好人好者點會輸錢"},{"pid":"393b011e4a0e83593c8345dd6c5b80bab8c84de1","tid":1045191,"uid":4139,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"7faf95c78965329a3d7c584a3bb7a8efacaf045a","tid":1045191,"uid":21423,"like":17,"dislike":4,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T12:22:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T05:30:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/04/132926_903558c260d616ecd53c744932e8bb4e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F04%2F132926_903558c260d616ecd53c744932e8bb4e.png&h=963779e8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03